snippet.title: Super Mario Bros. 3 Mix - NES Hack Gameplay - Part 1 / 5
snippet.description:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/gorillagames

Max of Gamesquad Squad playing Super Mario Bros. 3 Mix, on my NES console.
This is a hacked rom of the original Super Mario Bros. 3 NES game which has been converted to fit onto an NES cartridge.
This is arguably the best game hack anyone has ever made for this game. It's a complete remix of the game and then some; containing elements from nearly every Mario Bros. game to date.
Go to:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/gorillagames
if you are interested in buying this cart.
